      • PRIORITY_HIGH

      • PRIORITY_MEDIUM

        static final int PRIORITY_MEDIUM
        Uses a single thread to execute processes sequentially. Assumes that processes will complete in a reasonable time so that other processes do not have to wait long.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PRIORITY_LOW

        static final int PRIORITY_LOW
        Uses a single thread to execute processes sequentially. Assumes that processes can wait indefinately to run without consequence.
